!> reference: [https://doi.org/10.1021/ct5001268](https://doi.org/10.1021/ct5001268)
!> reference: [https://doi.org/10.1103/PhysRevB.94.165109](https://doi.org/10.1103/PhysRevB.94.165109)
! ***************************************************************************************************
